Summary: Not seen in Orlando, but rather on a National Geographic HD documentary.
divs: Sighting DetailsOn the National Geographic HD Channel Documentary called: "Is It Real? Atlantis" an interview was taking place in front of a Mayan Temple. In the background, near the temple, for about 3 seconds, a VERY CLEAR image of a UFO is seen entering the frame, then it appears to enter the temple, possibly? I have the show saved on my TIVO, if you would like further details about how long into the program this happens, or who was being interviewed, please contact me via email.
